#### Raspberry Pi Camera ####


#############

Rpi commands

#### to take picture ####

# standard pic
raspistill -o cam.jpg

# vertical flip / horizonatal flip
raspistill -vf -hf -o cam2.jpg


#### to record video ####

# Remember to use -hf and -vf to flip the image if required
raspivid -o video.h264 -t 10000

#### To play video ####
omxplayer video.h264




https://www.raspberrypi.org/learning/infrared-bird-box/